# Opam environment

Before running any `opam`, `ocaml`, `dune`, or other OCaml toolchain commands in this project, initialize the environment with:

```bash
export OPAMROOT="/lm/users/arul/.opam"
eval "$(opam env)"
```

Use this in shell sessions and when building, testing, or installing dependencies for this project.
